Example of object obtained from using the function base_PAM

Source: R/data_documentation.R
b_pam.Rd

An S3 object of class base_PAM. See functions prepare_base_PAM.

b_pam

Format

A list of 2 elements:

PAM

SpatialPolygonsDataFrame with 306 features

PAM_indices

a list of 11 elements

Examples

data("b_pam", package = "biosurvey")

print(b_pam)
